title: I Rated The Meal Deals Of Strangers | StreetSmart
description: In this video, Max Fosh goes around rating the meal deals of strangers on the street.
summary: Max Fosh rates the meal deals of strangers based on their presentation and value.
payoff: The humor comes from the reactions of the strangers as they are unexpectedly rated on their meal deals, leading to some awkward and funny interactions.
